         <abstract>
            <p>The stability of pseudospectral-Chebyshev methods is demonstrated for parabolic and hyperbolic problems with variable coefficients. The choice of collocation points is discussed. Numerical examples are given for the case of variable coefficient hyperbolic equations.</p>
          </abstract>
